### AlAshmar API - Auth Controller
### Base URL: http://localhost:5107
### =============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5107

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# Login
# POST /api/auth/login
# Returns a JWT token to use in all authenticated requests.
# Copy the token value from the response and set @authToken below.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@1234"
}

